  <metadata>
    <name>MUC-L2 — Austrian Tyrol Weekend Loop</name>
    <desc>Deploy from MUC and ride into the Austrian Tyrol. Hit Innsbruck and Hahntennjoch Pass — 1894m. Loop back to MUC over a packed 2–3 day weekend escape. No highways, just curves and elevation.</desc>
